  "prompt": "Who is Azor Ahai in Game of Thrones?",
  "response": "Azor Ahai is a legendary figure from the lore within the \"Game of Thrones\" series, particularly in George R.R. Martin's \"A Song of Ice and Fire\" books, upon which the TV series is based. According to prophecy, Azor Ahai is a hero destined to be reborn to defend the world against darkness, specifically against the threat posed by the Others, or White Walkers, as they are called in the show. This figure is said to wield a flaming sword called Lightbringer, which was forged through a great sacrifice.\n\nThroughout both the books and the television series, several characters are speculated to be the reincarnation of Azor Ahai, including Jon Snow, Daenerys Targaryen, and Stannis Baratheon, among others. However, the series does not explicitly confirm who Azor Ahai is, leaving it open to interpretation and speculation by the audience.",
